t the stanford ticket office cannot be responsible for the timeliness of delivery by the postal service donate in person the stanford ticket office is located on the second floor of tresidder memorial union on the stanford university campus donations can be made during normal business hours monday friday 10 00 am 5 00 pm saturday noon 4 00 pm please note tickets are not refundable tickets cannot be donated by phone or by email should you wish to exchange your tickets rather than donate them please note the procedures for ticket exchanges exchanges are free for partners of $125 and above and for full and mini subscribers for single performance purchases there is a $4.00 per ticket handling charge press info faq contact us privacy & legal site developed by mark hurty stanford lively arts tickets 650 725 arts email ticketorders stanford edu admin office 650 723 2551 email livelyarts stanford edu stanford university 425 santa teresa street mc 2250 stanford ca 94305 copyright 2000 2012 stanford lively arts like us on facebook watch us on vimeo follow us on twitter
